<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠١ - <span class="c3">{القارِعَة}</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{كَالْفَرَاشِ الْمَبْثُوثِ}</span>: كَغَوْغَاءِ الْجَرَادِ يَرْكَبُ بَعضُهُ بَعْضًا، كَذَلِكَ النَّاسُ يَجُولُ بَعْضُهُم فِي بَعْضٍ. <span class="c3">{كَالْعِهْنِ}</span>: كَأَلْوَانِ الْعِهْنِ.<span class="c5"> وَقَرَأَ عَبْدُ اللهِ:</span> <span class="c2">(كَالصُّوفِ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(والقارعة)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١٠٢ - <span class="c3">{أَلْهَاكُمُ}</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاس:</span> <span class="c3">{التَّكَاثُرُ}</span>: مِنَ الأَموَالِ وَالأَوْلَادِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(و <span class="c3">{أَلْهَاكُمُ}</span> <span class="c4">[التكاثر:١]</span>)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>* * *<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>[١٠٣ - <span class="c3">{والعصر}</span>]<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ يَحيَى:</span> الدَّهْرُ أَقْسَمَ بِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
